                "text": "Thanks! This looks super interesting - I was thinking and searching along the lines of \"data science\", but I completely missed all the work around relational data querying, even though that is exactly what I was looking for. This is a super interesting paper and the references in the literature are fantastic too.\n\nThe other interesting thing I cam across in the meantime is Wrex ("
